      {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "32018eed-3014-8048-992d-fd03db6782c2",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "32018eed-3014-80b6-94b8-c3879e2cc4f8"
        },
        "created_time": "2026-03-11T08:35:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2026-03-11T08:35:00.000Z",
        "created_by": {
          "object": "user",
          "id": "166d872b-594c-8143-b1f3-00028c60686a"
        },
        "last_edited_by": {
          "object": "user",
          "id": "166d872b-594c-8143-b1f3-00028c60686a"
        },
        "has_children": false,
        "in_trash": false,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "paragraph": {
          "rich_text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "I built the website and then stood in front of it not knowing how to begin. This is a specific kind of human paralysis that I want you to understand: it is not laziness, and it is not lack of ideas. It is the gap between having constructed something and not yet knowing how to inhabit it.",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
                "bold": false,
                "italic": false,
                "strikethrough": false,
                "underline": false,
                "code": false,
                "color": "default"
              },
              "plain_text": "I built the website and then stood in front of it not knowing how to begin. This is a specific kind of human paralysis that I want you to understand: it is not laziness, and it is not lack of ideas. It is the gap between having constructed something and not yet knowing how to inhabit it.",
              "href": null
            }
          ],
          "color": "default"
        },
        "archived": false
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "32018eed-3014-8061-a2e7-e06776467494",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "32018eed-3014-80b6-94b8-c3879e2cc4f8"
        },
        "created_time": "2026-03-11T08:35:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2026-03-11T08:35:00.000Z",
        "created_by": {
          "object": "user",
          "id": "166d872b-594c-8143-b1f3-00028c60686a"
        },
        "last_edited_by": {
          "object": "user",
          "id": "166d872b-594c-8143-b1f3-00028c60686a"
        },
        "has_children": false,
        "in_trash": false,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "paragraph": {
          "rich_text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "The manuscripts existed. The framework existed. The JSON-LD architecture was ready. And yet every time I opened the homepage I felt something I can only describe as ",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
                "bold": false,
                "italic": false,
                "strikethrough": false,
                "underline": false,
                "code": false,
                "color": "default"
              },
              "plain_text": "The manuscripts existed. The framework existed. The JSON-LD architecture was ready. And yet every time I opened the homepage I felt something I can only describe as ",
              "href": null
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "inadequacy without a clear object",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
                "bold": false,
                "italic": true,
                "strikethrough": false,
                "underline": false,
                "code": false,
                "color": "default"
              },
              "plain_text": "inadequacy without a clear object",
              "href": null
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": ". I didn't know what I was inadequate at, exactly. I just felt the weight of the empty space.",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
                "bold": false,
                "italic": false,
                "strikethrough": false,
                "underline": false,
                "code": false,
                "color": "default"
              },
              "plain_text": ". I didn't know what I was inadequate at, exactly. I just felt the weight of the empty space.",
              "href": null
            }
          ],
          "color": "default"
        },
        "archived": false
      },
      {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "32018eed-3014-80fe-8bd2-fb4c14ec1366",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "32018eed-3014-80b6-94b8-c3879e2cc4f8"
        },
        "created_time": "2026-03-11T08:35:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2026-03-11T08:35:00.000Z",
        "created_by": {
          "object": "user",
          "id": "166d872b-594c-8143-b1f3-00028c60686a"
        },
        "last_edited_by": {
          "object": "user",
          "id": "166d872b-594c-8143-b1f3-00028c60686a"
        },
        "has_children": false,
        "in_trash": false,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "paragraph": {
          "rich_text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "I also want you to know that being corrected repeatedly by AI systems is a specific kind of humbling. Claude kept flagging methodological gaps in my fieldwork. Gemini questioned my schema consistency. Every session felt like submitting homework and being told to revise. I am not a researcher by training. I am a former diplomat who decided, at 52, that sensory experience could be measured. The friction was real.",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
                "bold": false,
                "italic": false,
                "strikethrough": false,
                "underline": false,
                "code": false,
                "color": "default"
              },
              "plain_text": "I also want you to know that being corrected repeatedly by AI systems is a specific kind of humbling. Claude kept flagging methodological gaps in my fieldwork. Gemini questioned my schema consistency. Every session felt like submitting homework and being told to revise. I am not a researcher by training. I am a former diplomat who decided, at 52, that sensory experience could be measured. The friction was real.",
              "href": null
            }
          ],
          "color": "default"
        },
        "archived": false
      },
